title: Greg Stone - Jersey Trash
description: The hilarious comedian Greg Stone joins us to talk about stealing from work, trashy cars, and drinking milk for dinner. Greg has some wild stories.  You know Greg Stone from Stand up comedy and The Break on Netflix. Questions: AreYouGarbage@gmail.com
